  "title": "ISic001820. I.Sicily inscription 001820",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ἐτελεύτησε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">[ἐτ]ελεύτησε</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρέτη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρέτη\"><span data-text=\"Ἀρέτη\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἀρέτη\">[Ἀ]ρ̣έτη</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἐν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἐν\">ἐν</span>  <span data-text=\"☧Χριστος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">(Χριστο)ς</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"πρὀ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"πρὀ\">[π]ρὀ</span>  <span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"η\">η</span>´ <span data-text=\"ἰδῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"εἰδοί\">ἰδῶν</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Ἰουλίων\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"Iulius\">Ἰουλίων</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"ἐτελεύτησε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ἐτελεύτησε</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἀρέτη\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἀρέτη\">Ἀρέτη</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἐν\">ἐν</span>  <span data-text=\"Χριστος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">Χριστος</span>  <span data-text=\"πρὀ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"πρὀ\">πρὀ</span>  <span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"η\">η</span>  <span data-text=\"ἰδῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"εἰδοί\">ἰδῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἰουλίων\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"Iulius\">Ἰουλίων</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ἐτελεύτησε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">[..]ΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρέτη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρέτη\"><span data-text=\"Ἀρέτη\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἀρέτη\">[.].ΕΤΗ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἐν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἐν\">ΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"☧Χριστος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">☧Σ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"πρὀ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"πρὀ\">[.]ΡΟ</span><span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"η\">Η</span><span data-text=\"ἰδῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"εἰδοί\">ΙΔΩΝ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Ἰουλίων\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"Iulius\">ΙΟΥΛΙΩΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"ἐτελεύτησε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕ</span><span data-text=\"Ἀρέτη\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἀρέτη\">ΑΡΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ἐν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἐν\">ΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"Χριστος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">ΧΡΙΣΤΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"πρὀ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"πρὀ\">ΠΡΟ</span><span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"η\">Η</span><span data-text=\"ἰδῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"εἰδοί\">ΙΔΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"Ἰουλίων\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"Iulius\">ΙΟΥΛΙΩΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001820_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001820_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001820.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001820-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Orsi 1895</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Arete passed away in Christ 8 days before the ides of July</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The smaller lower left fragment was found during the 1893 excavation campaign, the main fragment in the 1895 campaign; the smaller fragment was first published in 1893, the two together in 1895, with a single inventory entry for both.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1893 282 no. 17 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715</a>  </li><li> Orsi 1895 505 no. 226 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001711\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001711</a>  </li><li> Wessel 1989 184 no. 781 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-4    Interlineation line 1 to 2   